Class PercentageSplit

  • java.lang.Object
    • meka.events.LogObject
      • meka.experiment.evaluators.AbstractEvaluator
        • meka.experiment.evaluators.PercentageSplit
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public class PercentageSplit
extends AbstractEvaluator
implements weka.core.Randomizable
    Evaluates the classifier on a percentage split. Order can be preserved.
